The Governing Council of the Ahmadu Bello University (ABU), Zaria yesterday announced Professor Kabir Bala as the new Vice Chancellor of the university with effect from 1st May, 2020. Daily Trust digged deep into the credentials of this erudite Professor who personally prefers to be called ‘Malam’. Below are top seventeen things to know about the incoming Vice Chancellor of one of Nigeria’s foremost tertiary institutions:  Prof Kabir Bala emerges ABU Vice-Chancellor Meet professor who prefers to be called ‘Malam’ ABU appoints Professor Kabir Bala as Vice Chancellor